title: Amanda Seyfried's Maternity Style in Photos | InStyle.com
text:
Bauer-Griffin/GC Images 1. February 09, 2017 
The pregnant actress showed off her casual-cool side while out in Los Angeles. For the coffee run, she opted for an on-trend graphic script T-shirt, skinny gray joggers, a butterfly-adorned crossbody bag, tortoiseshell sunnies, and quirky espadrille kicks. Lisa Mauceri/GC Images 2. February 1, 2017 
The expectant star was spotted on the set of her upcoming film First Reform , where she bundled up her growing bump in a stylish dress and cozy coat. A pair of black tights and matching booties finished her outfit. FameFlynet 3. December 14, 2016 
Seyfried was spotting taking her dog Finn out for a walk, covering up her baby bump with a baseball style Police T-shirt by Lauren Moshi (get a similar one from Junk Food Clothing ), black pants, and gray sneakers. FameFlynet 4. December 13, 2016 
We're loving this gingham look on Seyfried, who paired the cute Express sweater ($70; express.com ) with black leggings, black sunnies, and gray Converse sneakers ($50; nike.com ). BG005/Bauer-Griffin/GC Images 5. December 6, 2016 
The Mean Girls star was spotted out and about in Los Angeles, donning a simple outfit, featuring a black and white striped top under a black cardigan, black leggings, and brown lace-up boots (get a similar pair from Ugg ). JEDU/AKM-GSI 6. December 1, 2016 
In their first outing post-baby announcement, Seyfried and her fianc√© Thomas Sadoski took her pup, Finn, for a walk. Seyfried looked casual and cool in an all-black outfit, featuring a blazer-inspired coat (get a similar one from Revolve ), and black lace-up boots. Bauer-Griffin/GC Images 1 of 6 February 09, 2017
